        "$:/plugins/twpub/6d09b81e32b0d4bf/text/000000022": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/6d09b81e32b0d4bf/text/000000022",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-6d09b81e32b0d4bf-0fdc9a twpub-6d09b81e32b0d4bf-c3c16f twpub-6d09b81e32b0d4bf-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"blockquot\"><p class=\"smcap\"><big>To the Lords Spiritual and Temporal, and<br>\nthe Commons of the Parliament<br>\nof Great Britain.</big></p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/6d09b81e32b0d4bf/text/000000023": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/6d09b81e32b0d4bf/text/000000023",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-6d09b81e32b0d4bf-0fdc9a twpub-6d09b81e32b0d4bf-c3c16f twpub-6d09b81e32b0d4bf-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"blockquot\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/6d09b81e32b0d4bf/text/000000024": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/6d09b81e32b0d4bf/text/000000024",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-6d09b81e32b0d4bf-0fdc9a twpub-6d09b81e32b0d4bf-c3c16f twpub-6d09b81e32b0d4bf-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"blockquot\"><p><i>My Lords and Gentlemen</i>,</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/6d09b81e32b0d4bf/text/000000025": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/6d09b81e32b0d4bf/text/000000025",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-6d09b81e32b0d4bf-0fdc9a twpub-6d09b81e32b0d4bf-c3c16f twpub-6d09b81e32b0d4bf-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"blockquot\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/6d09b81e32b0d4bf/text/000000026": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/6d09b81e32b0d4bf/text/000000026",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-6d09b81e32b0d4bf-0fdc9a twpub-6d09b81e32b0d4bf-c3c16f twpub-6d09b81e32b0d4bf-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"blockquot\"><p>Permit me, with the greatest deference and respect, to lay at your feet the following genuine Narrative; the chief design of which is to excite in your august assemblies a sense of compassion for the miseries which the Slave-Trade has entailed on my unfortunate countrymen. By the horrors of that trade was I first torn away from all the tender connexions that were naturally dear to my heart; but these, through the mysterious ways of Providence, I ought to regard as infinitely more than compensated by the introduction I have thence obtained to the knowledge of the Christian religion, and of a nation which, by its liberal sentiments, its humanity, the glorious freedom of its government, and its proficiency in arts and sciences, has exalted the dignity of human nature.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/6d09b81e32b0d4bf/text/000000027": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/6d09b81e32b0d4bf/text/000000027",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-6d09b81e32b0d4bf-0fdc9a twpub-6d09b81e32b0d4bf-c3c16f twpub-6d09b81e32b0d4bf-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"blockquot\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/6d09b81e32b0d4bf/text/000000028": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/6d09b81e32b0d4bf/text/000000028",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-6d09b81e32b0d4bf-0fdc9a twpub-6d09b81e32b0d4bf-c3c16f twpub-6d09b81e32b0d4bf-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"blockquot\"><p>I am sensible I ought to entreat your pardon for addressing to you a work so wholly devoid of literary merit; but, as the production of an unlettered African, who is actuated by the hope of becoming an instrument towards the relief of his suffering countrymen, I trust that <i>such a man</i>, pleading in <i>such a cause</i>, will be acquitted of boldness and presumption.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/6d09b81e32b0d4bf/text/000000029": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/6d09b81e32b0d4bf/text/000000029",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-6d09b81e32b0d4bf-0fdc9a twpub-6d09b81e32b0d4bf-c3c16f twpub-6d09b81e32b0d4bf-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"blockquot\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/6d09b81e32b0d4bf/text/000000030": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/6d09b81e32b0d4bf/text/000000030",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-6d09b81e32b0d4bf-0fdc9a twpub-6d09b81e32b0d4bf-c3c16f twpub-6d09b81e32b0d4bf-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"blockquot\"><p>May the God of heaven inspire your hearts with peculiar benevolence on that important day when the question of Abolition is to be discussed, when thousands, in consequence of your Determination, are to look for Happiness or Misery!</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/6d09b81e32b0d4bf/text/000000031": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/6d09b81e32b0d4bf/text/000000031",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-6d09b81e32b0d4bf-0fdc9a twpub-6d09b81e32b0d4bf-c3c16f twpub-6d09b81e32b0d4bf-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"blockquot\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/6d09b81e32b0d4bf/text/000000032": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/6d09b81e32b0d4bf/text/000000032",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-6d09b81e32b0d4bf-0fdc9a twpub-6d09b81e32b0d4bf-c3c16f twpub-6d09b81e32b0d4bf-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"blockquot\"><p class=\"citation\">I am,                          <br>\n<span class=\"smcap\">My Lords and Gentlemen,</span>             <br>\nYour most obedient,  <br>\nAnd devoted humble servant,    <br>\n<span class=\"smcap\">Olaudah Equiano,</span><br>\n<span class=\"smcap\">or</span>           <br>\n<span class=\"smcap\">Gustavus Vassa.</span><br>\n<br></p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/6d09b81e32b0d4bf/text/000000033": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/6d09b81e32b0d4bf/text/000000033",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-6d09b81e32b0d4bf-0fdc9a twpub-6d09b81e32b0d4bf-c3c16f twpub-6d09b81e32b0d4bf-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"blockquot\">\n</div></div>"
        },
