            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-6d09b81e32b0d4bf-0fdc9a twpub-6d09b81e32b0d4bf-c3c16f twpub-6d09b81e32b0d4bf-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"footnotes\"><div class=\"footnote\"><p><a></a><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/6d09b81e32b0d4bf/text/000000104\"><span class=\"label\">[C]</span></$link> The bowl is earthen, curiously figured, to which a long reed is fixed as a tube. This tube is sometimes so long as to be born by one, and frequently out of grandeur by two boys.</p></div></div></div>"
        },
