            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-6d09b81e32b0d4bf-0fdc9a twpub-6d09b81e32b0d4bf-c3c16f twpub-6d09b81e32b0d4bf-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"blockquot\"><p>Howbeit, we must be cast upon a certain island;</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/6d09b81e32b0d4bf/text/000000344": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/6d09b81e32b0d4bf/text/000000344",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-6d09b81e32b0d4bf-0fdc9a twpub-6d09b81e32b0d4bf-c3c16f twpub-6d09b81e32b0d4bf-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"blockquot\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/6d09b81e32b0d4bf/text/000000345": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/6d09b81e32b0d4bf/text/000000345",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-6d09b81e32b0d4bf-0fdc9a twpub-6d09b81e32b0d4bf-c3c16f twpub-6d09b81e32b0d4bf-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"blockquot\"><p>Wherefore, sirs, be of good cheer: for I believe God, that it shall be even as it was told me.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/6d09b81e32b0d4bf/text/000000346": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/6d09b81e32b0d4bf/text/000000346",
